<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Todo App - Home</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/home.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <header>
        <h1>Welcome to <span style="color: aqua">Todo App</span></h1>
        <p>
          Your tasks, organized and optimized. Manage your to-do list
          effortlessly!
        </p>
      </header>

      <section class="about">
        <div data-coreui-toggle="rating" data-coreui-value="3"></div>
        <h2>About the App</h2>
        <p>
          The Todo App is a simple, user-friendly tool that helps you keep track
          of your tasks and stay organized. Whether it's a personal to-do list
          or a team project, Todo App is here to help you prioritize your tasks
          and improve your productivity. Create, edit, and delete tasks with
          just a few clicks. Never forget what you need to do again!
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="features">
        <h2>Key Features</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Create Tasks:</strong> Add new tasks with descriptions and
            due dates.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Mark Tasks as Completed:</strong> Easily mark tasks as
            completed and track your progress.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Edit and Delete Tasks:</strong> Modify or remove tasks at
            any time.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Organize Your Day:</strong> Prioritize your tasks and stay
            on top of your schedule.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="/signup" class="cta-button signup">Sign Up</a>
        <a href="/login" class="cta-button login">Login</a>
      </div>

      <footer>
        <p>Enjoy your day along with some work done!!</p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
